before the show. What's he doing?

17
00:01:46,690 --> 00:01:47,608
What is it?

18
00:01:48,317 --> 00:01:49,735
Smash!

19
00:01:57,743 --> 00:01:59,870
Both colors look good.

20
00:01:59,953 --> 00:02:01,496
-That's cool, too.
-It is.

21
00:02:01,622 --> 00:02:03,332
Okay. That's it.

22
00:02:03,582 --> 00:02:04,916
As for me...

23
00:02:07,169 --> 00:02:08,795
Red looks cool, too.

24
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:09,963
This one and...

25
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,923
<i>Mr. Kamiya...</i>

26
00:02:12,049 --> 00:02:15,510
<i>It was like he couldn't stop</i>
<i>punishing himself.</i>

27
00:02:16,845 --> 00:02:18,013
Take both of them.

28
00:02:18,305 --> 00:02:19,556
Thank you.

29
00:02:19,931 --> 00:02:22,267
-I'll pay for mine.
-I don't need your money.

30
00:02:22,434 --> 00:02:24,019
